 
<p>
  Maya Forstater, who was dismissed from work for maintaining that
  gender identities are meaningless and all that matters is a person's
  biological sex, has <a href="https://www.theguardian.com/society/2022/jul/06/maya-forstater-was-discriminated-against-over-gender-critical-beliefs-tribunal-rules">won a discrimination lawsuit</a>.
<p>
  I disagree with those views, but I defend her right to state views
  that disagree with mine.

 